As a marketing lead, I want to be able to download tweets with a certain industry hashtag, put them in a Google Natural Language API,
so that I can know what to focus on for my next advertisement. 
As an indie artist, I want to be able to track mentions of my name and their locations,
so that I can make schedule shows according to locations that will sell out.
As a tourist promoter, I want to be able to track mentions of my city and events, 
so that I can provide visitors with quick information about city events, or sell the information to magazines
As a retail industry executive, I want to be able to sort out information about trending styles based on twitter mentions, 
so that I can be ahead in bringing to market these exact styles
